  "description": "Two takeaway classics collide in this beef in black bean inspired burger. You'll pile aromatic lean beef patties in buttery brioche buns, with roasted pepper, and a rich black bean and onion gravy. Serve with nigella seed fries and crispy 'seaweed.' ",
